@startuml sequence-create-issue
title Диаграмма последовательности: создание новой задачи
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #F2F7FF

actor "Разработчик" as Dev
participant "Web-клиент" as Web
participant "JwtAuthGuard" as Guard
participant "TenantMiddleware" as TM
participant "IssuesController" as Ctrl
participant "IssuesService" as Svc
participant "EventEmitter2" as Bus
participant "IssuesGateway\n(WebSocket)" as WS
participant "NotificationsService" as Notif
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Dev -> Web : Заполняет форму\n«Создать задачу»
Web -> TM : POST /api/projects/:id/issues\nHost: acme.app.localhost\nAuthorization: Bearer JWT
TM -> TM : извлечь tenantId по slug
TM -> Guard : forward
Guard -> Guard : verify(JWT)
Guard -> Ctrl : forward (req.user, req.tenantId)
Ctrl -> Svc : create(projectId, tenantId, dto)
Svc -> DB : SELECT MAX("order") ...
DB --> Svc : maxOrder
Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO issues ... RETURNING *
DB --> Svc : Issue
Svc -> Bus : emit(issue.created, payload)
Svc --> Ctrl : Issue
Ctrl --> Web : 201 Created + Issue
Web --> Dev : Карточка появилась\nна доске

== Асинхронная обработка ==
Bus -> WS : on(issue.created)
WS -> Web : ws emit issue:created
Bus -> Notif : on(issue.created)
Notif -> DB : INSERT INTO notifications
Notif -> WS : ws emit notification:new

@enduml
